These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: nigerian, italian, french, indian
1. Nationality:italian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:indian is between Nationality:nigerian and Nationality:italian##2
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | nigerian | indian | italian | french |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: pineapple, blueberry, pepper, cranberry
1. Food:pineapple is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
2. Food:blueberry is in an odd position##4
3. Food:blueberry is on the left or right of Food:pineapple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | blueberry | pineapple | cranberry | pepper |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: satire, scientific, disaster, comedy
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:satire##3
2. Movie-Genre:satire is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:disaster is between Movie-Genre:comedy and Movie-Genre:scientific##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy | disaster | scientific |

