.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: lettuce, pumpkin, broccoli, corn
1. Food:pumpkin == Food:pumpkin##1
2. Food:corn is on the left or right of Food:broccoli##3
3. Food:broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:lettuce is in an even position##4
5. Food:corn is on the left of Food:pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | broccoli | corn | pumpkin | lettuce |

